        "content": "<p>On branch <code>private-noncomputable-abbrev-F</code>, <code>leanblueprint checkdecls</code> is failing with <code>F is missing</code>. I only need <code>F</code> in this file and currently I pollute the root namespace with it. How should I fix this? </p>\n<p>In the LaTeX we have</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"TeX\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">\\begin</span><span class=\"nb\">{</span>definition<span class=\"nb\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">\\lean</span><span class=\"nb\">{</span>F<span class=\"nb\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">\\label</span><span class=\"nb\">{</span>F<span class=\"nb\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">\\leanok</span>\n  If <span class=\"s\">$</span><span class=\"nb\">b</span><span class=\"nv\">\\in</span><span class=\"nb\"> B</span><span class=\"s\">$</span> then define the <span class=\"k\">\\emph</span><span class=\"nb\">{</span>characteristic polynomial<span class=\"nb\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"s\">$</span><span class=\"nb\">F_b</span><span class=\"s\">$</span> of <span class=\"s\">$</span><span class=\"nb\">b</span><span class=\"s\">$</span> to be <span class=\"s\">$</span><span class=\"nv\">\\prod</span><span class=\"nb\">_{g</span><span class=\"nv\">\\in</span><span class=\"nb\"> G}</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">X</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"nb\">g</span><span class=\"nv\">\\cdot</span><span class=\"nb\"> b</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"s\">$</span>.\n<span class=\"k\">\\end</span><span class=\"nb\">{</span>definition<span class=\"nb\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>and in the Lean we have</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">private</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">noncomputable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">abbrev</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∏ᶠ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">τ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">G</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">τ</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">•</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
